{"domain":"www.xenos.org","next_page_id":null,"url":"http://www.xenos.org/xsi/register.php","short_url":"http://rdd.me/xyahmays","author":null,"excerpt":"Xenos members register here Tuition Rates &#xA0; Full Conference One Day Adult $60.00 $30.00","direction":"ltr","word_count":124,"total_pages":0,"content":"<div><div id=\"page\">\n  <div id=\"page-inner\">\n    \n    \n     \n    \n\n    <div id=\"main\">\n      <div id=\"main-inner\" class=\"clear-block\">\n         \n        <div id=\"content\">\n          <div id=\"content-inner\">\n            <div id=\"content-header\"><img src=\"http://www.xenos.org/xsi/graphics/xsi14banner6-ns.png\" alt=\"Xenos Summer Institute\" width=\"600\"></div> \n            \n            <div id=\"content-area\"><div id=\"text\">\n\n        <div>\n        \n       \n       \n         <h3> Xenos members <a href=\"http://www.xenos.org/xsi/register.php?homegroup\">register here</a></h3>\n       \n        \n        <br>\n        \n\n        <div>\n        <h2>Tuition Rates </h2>\n        <table width=\"100%\">\n          <tr>\n            <th scope=\"col\">&#xA0;</th>\n            <th scope=\"col\">Full Conference</th>\n            <th scope=\"col\">One Day</th>\n          </tr>\n          <tr>\n            <th scope=\"row\">Adult</th>\n            <td>$60.00</td>\n            <td>$30.00</td>\n          </tr>\n          <tr>\n            <th scope=\"row\">Full-time Student</th>\n            <td>$20.00</td>\n            <td>$10.00</td>\n          </tr>\n          <tr>\n            <th colspan=\"3\">After June 27, 2014</th>\n          </tr>\n          <tr>\n            <th scope=\"row\">Adult</th>\n            <td>$70.00</td>\n            <td>$35.00</td>\n          </tr>\n          <tr>\n            <th scope=\"row\">Full-time Student</th>\n            <td>$20.00</td>\n            <td>$10.00</td>\n          </tr>\n        </table>\n        </div>\n        </div>\n\n        \n         \n        <p>Enter the names, email addresses and registration options for up to 4 people,<br>\n        then press the <em>\"Add Registrations and Check Out\"</em> button when you are finished.</p>\n        <p>You'll be taken to the Xenos online catalog to check out and pay for your registration(s). You can also register by phone at <strong>800-698-7884</strong>.</p>\n        \n        \n        \n        \n        <table>\n          <tr>\n            <th>First Name</th>\n            <th>Last Name</th>\n            <th>E-mail</th>\n            <th>Conference Length</th>\n            <th>Full-time Student?</th>\n          </tr>\n\t\t\t\t                                  <tr>\n            <td></td>\n            <td></td>\n            <td></td>\n            <td>\n            </td>\n            <td></td>\n          </tr>\n                  <tr>\n            <td></td>\n            <td></td>\n            <td></td>\n            <td>\n            </td>\n            <td></td>\n          </tr>\n                  <tr>\n            <td></td>\n            <td></td>\n            <td></td>\n            <td>\n            </td>\n            <td></td>\n          </tr>\n                  <tr>\n            <td></td>\n            <td></td>\n            <td></td>\n            <td>\n            </td>\n            <td></td>\n          </tr>\n                </table>\n        <h3> Groups of 5 or more <a href=\"http://www.xenos.org/xsi/register.php?group\">register here</a> for a discount.</h3>\n         <br>\n        <div>Please let us know if you have special needs like wheelchair seating or sign language interpretation. Just include them in the comments section at checkout - thanks!\n          \n        </div>\n        \n        \n    <br>\n    \n        \n    <br>\n    \n        \n    <br>\n    \n        \n    <br>\n    \n        \n      </div>\n      \n            \n              \n            </div> \n            \n          </div>\n        </div> \n      </div>\n    </div> \n    \n\n \n\n\n  </div>\n</div> \n</div>","date_published":null,"d